    "causal_summary": "The graph-metadata backfill generator refreshed z_future by default. Its tree walk in collectSpecFolders only skipped z_future under the --active-only flag, so a default run descended into z_future and the parser threw because z_future is not a supported specs root, and the walk over-reached. The fix adds z_future to the EXCLUDED_DIRS set so the walk unconditionally prunes the staging area, corrects the header comment, and rebuilds the dist, while z_archive stays included by default and skippable via --active-only.",
    "created_at": "2026-06-22T00:00:00.000Z",
